title: Princess Agent: The Sweet Country Girl’s Way to Glory - Novel Updates
tags: Ancient Times   Bickering Couple   Clever Protagonist   Female Protagonist   Late Romance   Transmigration
author: Qing Fei Yi   卿非意
description: Miao Yisheng calls off his wedding. However, the bride, Su Wanwan, is not sad at all because she is not Su Wanwan. She is an agent from Planet X. After a fierce battle, she died, and her soul passed into Su Wanwan's body. Although she has only lived with her current family for a short while, she loves them. She decides to make this life count and pull her new family out of poverty. The first thing on her to-do list is to make her parent divorce each other.>
